{"_id":"post-dcde9a66-9a70-4441-b7d8-5a5f7ba7a54a","_type":"post","title":"Community-Led Code Jams","slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"code-jams"},"body":[{"_key":"ec34fde0ff51","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"A few months ago, we created a new Discord channel - a real time chat app - for Repl.it. We've since expanded our user count to be well over 500. Our Discord server is community-driven - we have a team of three users who help us moderate the server and facilitate a culture of friendly collaboration and sharing knowledge. However, our favorite outcome of this community are the code jams.","_key":"ec34fde0ff510"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"8c02df4bd319","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Code jams are basically online hackathons that span from 24 to 48 hours long. Each code jam has a theme which is revealed to its participants at the beginning of the event. Each user creates a submission based on the given theme; their submissions must be created and developed during the code jam (no using previous work).","_key":"8c02df4bd3190"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"eecee98f2e11","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"From these code jams, we've seen some incredible work created in a small amount of time. But more importantly, we've been able to see the best of our community through its interactions. Participants had their own #code-jam channel in which they could discuss the jam, their work, and any questions that they had. Make no mistake - it was a competition - and they wanted to win. But that didn't stop them from helping out their fellow competitors debug their programs, provide feedback, and test our their work.","_key":"eecee98f2e110"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"85510982a3ff","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Our latest code jam wrapped up last weekend, where users made single player games. The winner was clear - ","_key":"85510982a3ff0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["7529ea537125"],"text":"@theangryepicbanana","_key":"85510982a3ff1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" made a game called ","_key":"85510982a3ff2"},{"_type":"span","marks":["bb15b216163e"],"text":"Switch","_key":"85510982a3ff3"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" using p5.js. The mods who graded this game thought it was original, fun to play, and well polished.","_key":"85510982a3ff4"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"7529ea537125","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.it/@theangryepicbanana"},{"_key":"bb15b216163e","_type":"link","href":"https://CodeJam2--theangryepicbanana.repl.co"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"3c69dfcf978b","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"A demonstration of the game is below - or play it yourself ","_key":"3c69dfcf978b0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["68defdcfcf1e"],"text":"here","_key":"3c69dfcf978b1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"!","_key":"3c69dfcf978b2"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"68defdcfcf1e","_type":"link","href":"https://CodeJam2--theangryepicbanana.repl.co"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"cd9e831a647e","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Other sample submissions, in no particular order:","_key":"cd9e831a647e0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"286891d4ea23","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["ef30a05997d2"],"text":"MurderousDungeon","_key":"286891d4ea230"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" by ","_key":"286891d4ea231"},{"_type":"span","marks":["3cba0ce09054"],"text":"@HappyFakeboulde","_key":"286891d4ea232"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"ef30a05997d2","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.it/@HappyFakeboulde/MurderousDungeon"},{"_key":"3cba0ce09054","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.it/@HappyFakeboulde"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"6b880ff4620a","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["8ae8545003d2"],"text":"Missile Commander","_key":"6b880ff4620a0"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" by ","_key":"6b880ff4620a1"},{"_type":"span","marks":["d8ff54bdb530"],"text":"@TrevorBarron","_key":"6b880ff4620a2"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"8ae8545003d2","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.it/@TrevorBarron/CodeJam2"},{"_key":"d8ff54bdb530","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.it/@TrevorBarron"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"3cc1a201c72c","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["d15792f41ca4"],"text":"Bomb Diffuser","_key":"3cc1a201c72c0"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" by ","_key":"3cc1a201c72c1"},{"_type":"span","marks":["f8f146156e24"],"text":"@Vandesm14","_key":"3cc1a201c72c2"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"d15792f41ca4","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.it/@Vandesm14/CodeJam2"},{"_key":"f8f146156e24","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.it/@Vandesm14"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"4e75705b6834","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"These code jams were organized, executed, and judged entirely by the Discord moderators - we would like to personally thank ","_key":"4e75705b68340"},{"_type":"span","marks":["e1867c392f8d"],"text":"@Mosrod","_key":"4e75705b68341"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" and ","_key":"4e75705b68342"},{"_type":"span","marks":["81e384b44efb"],"text":"@21natzil","_key":"4e75705b68343"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" (Zwack) for their hard work.","_key":"4e75705b68344"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"e1867c392f8d","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.it/@Mosrod"},{"_key":"81e384b44efb","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.it/@21natzil"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"bae79f52d6de","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"If you're interested in joining us in our next code jam sometime in the next month, join our Discord server with ","_key":"bae79f52d6de0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["8202744ac65d"],"text":"this invite link","_key":"bae79f52d6de1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"!","_key":"bae79f52d6de2"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"8202744ac65d","_type":"link","href":"https://discord.gg/346Tapr"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"}],"publishedAt":"2018-08-10T00:00:00.000Z"}